overview: On February 11th GCW presents Jersey J-Cup live on FITE+ straight from White Eagle Hall in Jersey City! The event will be in 2 sessions, and the first 15 entrants in Session one have been announced, here they are:  Mike Bailey  Alex Shelley  Jonathan Gresham  Komander  Arez  Jack Cartwheel  Joey Janela  Jordan Oliver  Cole Radrick  Tony Deppen  Blake Christian  Alec Price  Billie Starkz  Charlie Starboy  Lio Rush
title: GCW Jersey J-Cup, Session 1
